N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 206.1 - Power of Commission to control combative sports and professional wrestling

State Regulations

No combative sport or professional wrestling contest or
exhibition shall be held within this State except in accordance with law and
the rules of the Commission. Notes
